-You started it.

594
00:27:25,211 --> 00:27:26,612
He can drink the milk.

595
00:27:27,546 --> 00:27:28,547
But we all watch.

596
00:27:28,714 --> 00:27:30,149
Will your mustache be okay?

597
00:27:30,816 --> 00:27:31,984
It's no problem.

598
00:27:33,085 --> 00:27:33,986
Wait, Kurochan.

599
00:27:37,356 --> 00:27:39,125
-It was your idea.
-It was my idea.

600
00:27:39,191 --> 00:27:41,861
