644
00:29:36,675 --> 00:29:37,843
Stop being so fussy.

645
00:29:37,977 --> 00:29:40,246
-There's meat juice on my jacket.
-Don't fret.

646
00:29:42,748 --> 00:29:44,550
Is that an expensive jacket?

647
00:29:52,424 --> 00:29:54,493
I was wondering if it was expensive.

648
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:57,363
You always seem to get worried about
