00:30:25,224 --> 00:30:27,560
-Wait a minute.
-You can keep your clothes on.

663
00:30:27,626 --> 00:30:29,094
Straighten up.

664
00:30:29,161 --> 00:30:30,229
Keep your clothes on.

665
00:30:30,829 --> 00:30:32,531
-Keep them on.
-There's Haranishi.

666
00:30:33,566 --> 00:30:35,734
-It's Haranishi.
