667
00:30:35,801 --> 00:30:36,735
Wait a minute.

668
00:30:36,802 --> 00:30:39,171
I'm your senior.
We've known each for so long.

669
00:30:39,238 --> 00:30:41,073
-You can't talk like that.
-But I...

670
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:43,409
I won't allow it. Stand at this angle.

671
00:30:43,475 --> 00:30:44,476
Really, don't...

672
00:30:44,543 --> 00:30:46,011
-I'm scared.
-What's going on?

673
00:30:50,583 --> 00:30:51,550
Ouch!

674
00:30:52,785 --> 00:30:53,652
He's crying.

675
00:30:54,486 --> 00:30:56,288
