676
00:30:56,889 --> 00:30:58,557
-A grown adult.
-He's like Chaplin.

677
00:30:59,558 --> 00:31:01,060
It hurt even over his clothes.

678
00:31:01,126 --> 00:31:02,394
You and your big mouth.

679
00:31:02,628 --> 00:31:05,431
-I was cooking the meat for you guys.
-You're right.

680
00:31:05,564 --> 00:31:06,465
He deserved it.

681
00:31:06,532 --> 00:31:08,200
He always gets so fussy.

682
00:31:08,801 --> 00:31:09,868
You're still going?

683
00:31:10,302 --> 00:31:11,804
Miyasako, seriously.

684
00:31:12,238 --> 00:31:13,706
You always try to show off.

685
00:31:17,576 --> 00:31:18,611
Sit down.

686
00:31:20,379 --> 00:31:21,547
-Sit.
-What will you do?

687
00:31:21,614 --> 00:31:22,548
Just sit down.

688
00:31:23,382 --> 00:31:25,017
