691
00:31:35,027 --> 00:31:36,495
That was a really scary one.

692
00:31:36,629 --> 00:31:38,230
That was... He flipped.

693
00:31:38,998 --> 00:31:40,599
-He lost it.
-Scary.

694
00:31:42,301 --> 00:31:43,302
Fujimoto!

695
00:31:44,203 --> 00:31:45,704
He's doing it again.

696
00:31:59,585 --> 00:32:01,086
How cute. Just like a cat.

697
00:32:07,459 --> 00:32:10,329
-You shouldn't have glared at him.
-It's your fault.

698
00:32:13,465 --> 00:32:14,500
Fujimoto...

699
00:32:14,566 --> 00:32:16,335
-You're making it worse.
-Stop it.

700
00:32:16,402 --> 00:32:18,504
