708
00:33:02,381 --> 00:33:03,482
Please.

709
00:33:04,416 --> 00:33:06,318
-Keep it friendly, guys.
-Sure.

710
00:33:06,618 --> 00:33:08,620
-I'll cook the meat.
-Thank you.

711
00:33:08,721 --> 00:33:10,289
-They reconciled.
-Sorry.

712
00:33:10,422 --> 00:33:12,825
Did you fool around like that
when you were in Tenso?

713
00:33:14,226 --> 00:33:15,961
