715
00:33:19,164 --> 00:33:21,934
-That takes me back.
-But now, my bones are out of place.

716
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,302
Especially in my skull.

717
00:33:23,635 --> 00:33:25,270
He has a sadistic side, right?

718
00:33:25,571 --> 00:33:27,573
Toward comedians and mistresses.

719
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:29,007
Mistresses?

720
00:33:29,141 --> 00:33:31,143
