721
00:33:33,512 --> 00:33:36,582
-Do you do that to women, too?
-I heard he was kind.

722
00:33:36,648 --> 00:33:37,883
He is kind.

723
00:33:38,117 --> 00:33:39,585
Very kind. But...

724
00:33:41,453 --> 00:33:42,654
When he's in bed...

725
00:33:42,988 --> 00:33:44,056
What?

726
00:33:45,491 --> 00:33:47,259
Are you starting something again?

727
00:33:50,696 --> 00:33:52,831
