the skin here would be all saggy.

751
00:35:11,844 --> 00:35:14,346
What would you say when it bounced back?

752
00:35:14,413 --> 00:35:15,747
Is that another oogiri?

753
00:35:16,648 --> 00:35:18,150
That was the topic.

754
00:35:20,118 --> 00:35:21,954
Please don't make me do it.

755
00:35:23,055 --> 00:35:26,425
What do you say after your jaw drops
to the floor and bounces back?

756
00:35:26,625 --> 00:35:27,793
Ginkaku.

757
00:35:29,962 --> 00:35:31,096
What...

758
00:35:32,264 --> 00:35:33,599
What does that mean?

759
00:35:35,234 --> 00:35:38,303
What do you say after your jaw drops
to the floor and bounces back?

760
00:35:38,370 --> 00:35:39,204
I love you.

761
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:43,542
Quit making that noise.

762
00:35:44,810 --> 00:35:47,145
