"I love you" to "sizzle."

763
00:35:47,212 --> 00:35:48,780
I think it's the perfect sound.

764
00:35:49,014 --> 00:35:51,250
That must have come close.

765
00:35:52,718 --> 00:35:54,553
-Couldn't be helped.
-It was great.

766
00:35:54,620 --> 00:35:56,255
Wow. It barely fits.

767
00:35:56,388 --> 00:35:57,489
That's sizzling.

768
00:35:58,891 --> 00:36:00,325
Is rare okay?

769
