I nearly vomited.

816
00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:45,237
-You laughed at the sliminess?
-I laughed at the sliminess...

817
00:41:45,303 --> 00:41:46,838
Did I really laugh?

818
00:41:47,706 --> 00:41:48,874
What happened?

819
00:41:49,207 --> 00:41:51,009
Really! It was so slimy...

820
00:41:51,076 --> 00:41:53,578
Okay, I'll make that an orange card.

821
00:41:54,646 --> 00:41:56,314
Why did I put that in my mouth?

822
00:41:56,648 --> 00:41:58,250
So, well...

823
00:41:58,817 --> 00:42:01,086
Iio will be eliminated with his next card.

824
00:42:01,152 --> 00:42:02,454
I'm sorry.

825
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:04,189
Putting that in your mouth was gutsy.

826
00:42:04,356 --> 00:42:07,559
While I was watching in the back,
what impressed me the most was

827
00:42:07,692 --> 00:42:10,195
after you gave an answer to the oogiri,

828
00:42:10,262 --> 00:42:11,930
the meat went "sizzle."

829
00:42:14,366 --> 00:42:17,469
What do you say after your jaw drops
to the floor and bounces back?

830
00:42:17,535 --> 00:42:18,370
I love you.

831
00:42:21,273 --> 00:42:22,874
Quit making that noise.

832
00:42:23,975 --> 00:42:26,311
